casebody.data:
Fourth Department,

October, 1946.

(October 2, 1946.) John Critelli et al., Respondents, v. John Griswold, Appellant.

Order affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements. All concur. (The order denies defendant’s motion to vacate a warrant of dispossession in a summary proceeding.) Present — Taylor, P. J., Harris, McCurn and Larkin, JJ.
